<html xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_3.xsd">
<body>
    <h1>Activation Request Parameters (1)</h1>

    A render request can include query parameters in key=value fashion. To make a PageLink include query parameters, use its <code>parameters</code> parameter.

    <div class="eg">
        <t:pagelink t:page="ActivationRequestParameters2" t:parameters="queryParams">Show Person ${personId}</t:pagelink><br/>
    </div>

    That link will have a URL like this: <code>http://localhost:8080/activationrequestparameters2?personid=1</code><br/><br/>

    Click the link above to learn more.<br/><br/>
</body>
</html>